.TP
IdleDelay [int]
Delay between frames in miliseconds when in idle
.TP
ColorByExtension [bool]
Enable coloring files by its extensions
.TP
UpdateFile [bool]
Enable updating file information when scrolling
.TP
SizeInBytes [bool]
